  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/66119897effe97c9a0727934ad06a89c.webp?t=1726545611\" width=508 height=61 /></span><br><br>Conquer complex and comical fast-paced grid-based combat as Wren and Chloe, an unlikely duo about to discover just how much they don't know about the world of Deitrus. An Hour Long Action RPG with a Non-Linear Narrative.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/d4fee1f41267d539570d96b117cf6c0a.poster.avif?t=1726545611\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/d4fee1f41267d539570d96b117cf6c0a.webm?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/d4fee1f41267d539570d96b117cf6c0a.mp4?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fast-Paced Grid-Based Action</strong><br>Duke it out in a unique and deep combat system unlike any other. Dodge enemy's blows and respond in kind with one of your character's signature moves. From slicing swords to electric orbs, there's many play styles to choose from.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/ad84c1c70a2c3572431955609dab133e.poster.avif?t=1726545611\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/ad84c1c70a2c3572431955609dab133e.webm?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/ad84c1c70a2c3572431955609dab133e.mp4?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>An Island of Mystery</strong><br>Explore the furthest reaches of the island of Deitrus, from the crimson Forest of Fire to the dark caverns of tvCave... and perhaps more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/26c396e3048c8793879aa69d02ea5b49.poster.avif?t=1726545611\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/26c396e3048c8793879aa69d02ea5b49.webm?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/26c396e3048c8793879aa69d02ea5b49.mp4?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Masterful Sound</strong><br>A full soundtrack that brings atmosphere and emotion to the various locales, story beats, and moments of heart pounding tension!",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/66119897effe97c9a0727934ad06a89c.webp?t=1726545611\" width=508 height=61 /></span><br><br>Conquer complex and comical fast-paced grid-based combat as Wren and Chloe, an unlikely duo about to discover just how much they don't know about the world of Deitrus. An Hour Long Action RPG with a Non-Linear Narrative.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/d4fee1f41267d539570d96b117cf6c0a.poster.avif?t=1726545611\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/d4fee1f41267d539570d96b117cf6c0a.webm?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/d4fee1f41267d539570d96b117cf6c0a.mp4?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Fast-Paced Grid-Based Action</strong><br>Duke it out in a unique and deep combat system unlike any other. Dodge enemy's blows and respond in kind with one of your character's signature moves. From slicing swords to electric orbs, there's many play styles to choose from.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/ad84c1c70a2c3572431955609dab133e.poster.avif?t=1726545611\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/ad84c1c70a2c3572431955609dab133e.webm?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/ad84c1c70a2c3572431955609dab133e.mp4?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>An Island of Mystery</strong><br>Explore the furthest reaches of the island of Deitrus, from the crimson Forest of Fire to the dark caverns of tvCave... and perhaps more.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/26c396e3048c8793879aa69d02ea5b49.poster.avif?t=1726545611\" width=536 height=302 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/26c396e3048c8793879aa69d02ea5b49.webm?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1860140/extras/26c396e3048c8793879aa69d02ea5b49.mp4?t=1726545611\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Masterful Sound</strong><br>A full soundtrack that brings atmosphere and emotion to the various locales, story beats, and moments of heart pounding tension!",
